CONTRIBUTING

I'm in a continuous process of learning Perl, a very challenging
process, I can say, certainly one of the attributes that makes Perl my
preferred choice of the programming language to use.  That is why if
one thinks that I don't use properly the modules and/or follow the
patterns for implementing MVC and has the patience to explain why and
how it thinks is better in his way, please let me know.  Thank you.


INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make test
    make install


SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the
perldoc command.

    perldoc Tpda3


